      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just that talking or seeing someone doesn't actually change the physical reality of it. the doctors say there's nothing more they can do. it's not even a mental thing, it's just... this constant, unrelenting agony. it feels like there's no point to any of this anymore. i'm just existing to feel pain.",
